thread.title: Autumn Cyler
thread.title_full: Elevate Styles reviewed by Autumn Cyler

author: Autumn Cyler
title: Autumn Cyler
text: Elevated style came through in a pinch for me. I had ordered a wig for my 30th wedding anniversary and it wasn't going to work out. I ordered 2 wigs from Elevates on Sunday and I got them Tuesday.! Both wigs were beautiful. I'll use them for all my wig purchases in the future.
